Package com.github.webapp_minifier.replacer

Contains classes that handle parsing HTML and replacing content within those files.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NodeHandler
    Handler for nodes in an HTML document.
    TagReplacer
    Implementations of this interface aid in the modification of original HTML files by replacing tags and/or values as directed by the NodeHandler.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JsoupTagReplacer
    This class is a TagReplacer implementation that uses the jsoup library.
    TagReplacerFactory  
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ReplacerException
    ReplacerException is a runtime exception that is thrown when an error occurs during HTML parsing or tag replacement.
